content:
Abiyaa thannude kooril ni-nnulllloraachaaryan
Aharonyasthree elishubaa-sahitham nivasichu
/tdaivasamaksham-neethi labhichavaraayu
/tthan kalppanayil thalpparamaanasaraayu
Vedangallumee dampathikall-paalichennaalum
Saakshaal santathisaubhaagyam-hanta labhichilla.
/thaaleluyyaa-avallthan vandhyathayaal.
